"Live Laugh Loathe" Unisex Graphic Tee

~~How to Order~~
1)	Please carefully read and review all photos in the listing above. 
2)	Choosing your shirt size – a helpful technique: Go to your closet and find your favorite, best fitting Tee. Follow the lines in the size chart photos above and measure your shirt. Use those measurements as a guide for choosing your size when purchasing. That way, you have an idea if the size you are choosing will be more form fitting or looser than your favorite Tee. 
3)	Click “Add to Cart”. You can always go back to add more product from here.
4)	Click “Proceed to Checkout” when finished browsing.

~~About the Shirts~~
•	Our Unisex shirts fit like a well-loved Tee. They feature a comfortable crew neck, double-stitching on the neckline and sleeves, shoulder-to-shoulder taping, and are quarter turned to avoid creasing down the center. Pre-shrunk to remain true to size. 
•	It’s a thicker heavier cotton for a durability that will last but is still super soft and comfy for an everyday wear. 
•	100% ring-spun cotton
•	Sport Grey is 90% ring-spun cotton and 10% polyester.
•	Dark Heather is 65% polyester and 35% cotton.

~~Care Instructions~~ 
•	Wash item inside out in cold water.
•	Do not bleach.
•	Do not dry clean. 
•	Do not iron directly on the shirt design.

~~Production and Shipping~~
•	All of our shirts are made to order, printed and shipped right here in the United States.
•	Processing time is 5-9 days. First Class Shipping 2-5 business days (after processing time). 
•	If you need your items sooner, please upgrade shipping when ordering and we’ll make sure rush it to your door!
•	Please note that while we do accept cancelations, they need to be submitted within 12 hours of the original time of purchase.

results.title: Wrap bracelet with personalised message. Hand stamped to order. Range of colours available. Recycled/ up-cycled t-shirt yarn
results.description:
Stamped to order, this bracelet is a lovely gift for any boho fan. Popular for festivals and every day wear, this beautiful personalised gift is sure to be appreciated by both women or men regardless of age.

This tag comes on 120cm of jersey yarn so that you can tie it as desired (I recommend a simple knot). The yarn is leftover t-shirt material from the fabric industry, cut into strips to make the cord so is a great up-cycled product for the environmentally conscious. 

Wording can be chosen to suit. I can use a larger tag if more words are required. 

Due to the nature of hand stamping on aluminium (which is a light weight material), there will often be differences in the depth of the hand stamped letters/ pictures, the letters/ pictures may have a slight difference in spacing and the letters may not always be straight.. However I will do my best to make it the best I can as I want you to use it! There will also be slight indentation on the back, which is normal even though all blanks are at least 1.5mm thick. 
Please check out the other listings in my store at lovebeauxdesigns.etsy.com.
